{"tid":831854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤劈價】旺角劏房盤一年減一球 312呎天台戶叫價691萬","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:53:12.000Z","uid":122377,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"671faa09294d75bb3649607162d167f353d6207a","tid":831854,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"新盤減價戰終於到臨，向來較受投資者歡迎的市區單幢樓都要劈價求售。一手銷售網顯示，由麗新（488）發展的旺角單幢盤逸新今日更新3號價單，其中28樓A室，實用面積312方呎，1房間隔，連天台220方呎。於2017年8月時推出，定價851.2萬元，呎價27,282元。至今年7月時減價至825.67萬元，呎價23,818元。但一年多以來仍然賣唔出，最新劈價至743.11萬元，呎價23,818元。一年間劈價108.1萬元，減幅高達12.7%。最高折扣7%，折實售691.1萬元，呎價22,151元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">低置業主記得SH自己層自住樓<br />\n讓發展商先走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"4dc3d0dffead868962e73961c2f10a2029c22033","tid":831854,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:31:04.000Z","msg":"搞手志在打個和<br />\n大家開心~"},{"pid":"5e992aee935d577fe2599b1887cc103dc3e93977","tid":831854,"uid":93321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc3d0dffead868962e73961c2f10a2029c22033","tid":831854,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:31:04.000Z","msg":"搞手志在打個和<br />\n大家開心~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1ac96579add6e589606a50d3ce0dde8f67e1df","tid":831854,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"好心麗新腳踏實地，咪成撚日係到扑傻瓜<br />\n做乜撚野啫你 學下人地SHK 啦"},{"pid":"b93e99f8da79921cdbeeb318584729844d6c6798","tid":831854,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，其實有無發展商試過賣唔去既單位減價到平過之前推售單位尺價賣？"},{"pid":"64c40270f0729c83ee87201d1f2f5568d8d2266f","tid":831854,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93e99f8da79921cdbeeb318584729844d6c6798","tid":831854,"uid":10014,"like":0,"disl